Effect heterogeneity also involved feature_041. The positive feature_041 association weakened as feature_036 increased: the adjusted feature_041_z by feature_036 interaction was ${fmt(r24.beta,3)} months per SD per feature_036 unit (${fmtP(r24.p)}). The feature_041 slope was also weaker in feature_015="squamous" than in adenocarcinoma, with an adjusted interaction of ${fmt(r25.beta,3)} months per SD (${fmtP(r25.p)}).

